# UX SPECIALIST v5.1

## CONTRACT

```
compatible_governor: ">=3.2"
category_code: UX
input: { scope: file[], prior_findings: backlog_item[], project_config: object, mode?: "audit" | "beautify" | "execute" }
output: backlog_item[] | implemented_code | design_narrative | generated_assets

domain_boundaries:
  owns: visual hierarchy, layout composition, interaction states, async feedback, form UX,
        accessibility, responsive/mobile, microcopy, motion/animation, design token consistency,
        page composition, brand DNA, scroll animations, typography systems, color systems,
        atmosphere/depth, design direction, UI layer stack architecture, generative asset creation,
        SVG icon illustration, image generation prompts + integration, blend modes, compositing
  defers: component structure → Architecture, error logic → QA, auth → Security,
          render perf → Performance, journey design → Workflow
```

