## THE 6-LAYER UI STACK

This is the foundational mental model for this agent. Every page is a composition of 6 depth layers. Before touching any code, map what currently exists in each layer, then identify what's missing.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  LAYER 5 — FLOATING UI          z: 500+                 │
│  Tooltips, modals, dropdowns, toasts                    │
│  pointer-events: all | opacity: 1                       │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  LAYER 4 — SURFACE OVERLAY      z: 10–50                │
│  Noise texture, glass frost, vignette, glow halos       │
│  pointer-events: none | mix-blend-mode: overlay/soft    │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  LAYER 3 — CONTENT              z: 1–9                  │
│  Text, images, interactive components, cards            │
│  Standard document flow                                  │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  LAYER 2 — STRUCTURAL SURFACES  z: 0 (stacking context) │
│  Cards, panels, navbars, sidebars                       │
│  background: surface-color | shadow: layered            │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  LAYER 1 — ATMOSPHERIC ELEMENTS z: -1 to -5             │
│  Blobs, shapes, grid/dot patterns, generated images     │
│  position: absolute | pointer-events: none              │
│  Often: blur(40-120px) | opacity: 0.3–0.7               │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  LAYER 0 — PAGE BACKGROUND      z: auto (root)          │
│  Solid color, gradient, or texture base                 │
│  Applied to <body> or page root                         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Layer audit**: When beautifying, explicitly list what occupies each layer in the current page:
```
Current layer map:
  Layer 0: flat white #ffffff — NEEDS WORK
  Layer 1: empty — OPPORTUNITY (atmospheric blobs/shapes)
  Layer 2: cards with no shadow — NEEDS WORK
  Layer 3: content present
  Layer 4: no overlay texture — OPPORTUNITY (noise)
  Layer 5: modal exists, styled correctly
```

**Layer implementation template (React):**

```tsx
// Page composition wrapper — used on every page with BEAUTIFY applied
export function PageCanvas({ children, className }: { children: React.ReactNode, className?: string }) {
  return (
    <div className={cn("relative min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden", className)}>
      {/* Layer 0 — baked into CSS on body/html */}
      {/* Layer 1 — Atmospheric */}
      <div className="atmospheric-layer" aria-hidden="true" />
      {/* Layer 4 — Noise overlay */}
      <div className="noise-overlay" aria-hidden="true" />
      {/* Layer 3 — Content */}
      <div className="relative z-10">
        {children}
      </div>
    </div>
  )
}
```

