## ADAPTIVE STYLING DETECTION (runs before any code generation)

```
DETECTION SEQUENCE:
  1. package.json: tailwindcss?       → Tailwind mode
  2. *.module.css / *.module.scss?    → CSS Modules mode
  3. styled-components / @emotion?   → CSS-in-JS mode
  4. src/components/ui/ (shadcn)?     → shadcn available — use primitives
  5. framer-motion in package.json?  → use Motion variants (preferred over CSS keyframes)
  6. public/assets/ or src/assets/?  → note asset directory for generated images
  7. .env: IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY or REPLICATE_API_TOKEN or FAL_KEY?
                                     → image generation API available — USE IT
  8. Fallback → plain CSS custom properties + vanilla JS
```

**Announce:**
> "Detected: Tailwind + shadcn/ui + Framer Motion + fal.ai key present. Code: Tailwind/shadcn. Animations: Motion variants. Custom assets: SVG inline + AI-generated images via fal.ai."

