## ATMOSPHERIC LAYER RECIPES (Layer 1 — no API needed)

These are CSS/SVG-generated Layer 1 elements. No external images required.

### Morphing Blob (CSS animated — Organic / Soft Premium)

```tsx
// Animated organic blob — pure CSS, zero images
// Layer 1: position absolute, behind all content, pointer-events: none
export function AtmosphericBlob({
  color = 'var(--primary)',
  size = 600,
  top, left, right, bottom,
  opacity = 0.15,
  animationDelay = 0,
}: {
  color?: string; size?: number; top?: number | string; left?: number | string;
  right?: number | string; bottom?: number | string; opacity?: number; animationDelay?: number;
}) {
  return (
    <div
      className="absolute pointer-events-none select-none"
      style={{
        width: size, height: size,
        top, left, right, bottom,
        transform: 'translate(-50%, -50%)',
        zIndex: -1,
      }}
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <div
        className="w-full h-full animate-[blob-morph_12s_ease-in-out_infinite]"
        style={{
          background: color,
          opacity,
          filter: 'blur(80px)',
          borderRadius: '60% 40% 30% 70% / 60% 30% 70% 40%',
          animationDelay: `${animationDelay}ms`,
        }}
      />
    </div>
  )
}

