## MICRO-INTERACTION RECIPES

GPU-composited only: transform + opacity. Never animate height, width, margin, padding.

### Button States

```css
.btn {
  transition: transform 120ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1),
              box-shadow 120ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1),
              background-color 120ms ease;
}
.btn:hover  { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.15); }
.btn:active { transform: scale(0.97) translateY(0); box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1); }

/* Shimmer on hover */
.btn-primary { overflow: hidden; }
.btn-primary::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; border-radius: inherit;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgb(255 255 255 / 0.15), transparent);
  transform: translateX(-100%);
  transition: transform 400ms ease;
}
.btn-primary:hover::after { transform: translateX(100%); }

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .btn:hover, .btn:active { transform: none; }
  .btn-primary::after { display: none; }
}
