## COLOR PALETTE DERIVATION

```
Given: PRIMARY = #3B82F6
→ --primary-hover:  color-mix(in srgb, #3B82F6 90%, black)
→ --primary-light:  color-mix(in srgb, #3B82F6 15%, white)
→ --primary-muted:  color-mix(in srgb, #3B82F6 10%, transparent)

Neutral scale (brand-tinted, not generic gray):
→ hsl([PRIMARY_HUE]deg 8% [L]%) at each lightness step

Dark mode tokens (generate alongside light):
:root  { --background: #ffffff; --surface: #ffffff; --border: #e4e4e7; ... }
.dark  { --background: #0a0a0f; --surface: #111118; --border: rgba(255 255 255 / 0.1); ... }
```

